{"id":897717,"date":[{"year":1993,"month":2,"day":7}],"page":"8","source":"","region":"","masthead":"体育新闻","special_issue":"","column":"迎东亚运英语100句","genre":"","count":"291","ytitle":"","mtitle":"IN　THE　HOTEL　在宾馆","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"7.WHAT KIND OFROOM WOULD YOULIKE?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您想要什么样的房间?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Receptionist: Goodmorning.　Can I helpyou?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接待员:早上好。我能为您做些什么?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Lee:　Good morning.May I have a room?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李:早上好。有房间吗?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Receptionist:Certainly.　What kind ofroom would you like?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接待员:当然有。您想要什么样的房间?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Lee:　A twin bed room,please."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李:要一间双人房。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"Receptionist:Thank you."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接待员:谢谢。"}]}